      "label": "Condition",
      "value": "The right side has been torn off and the papyrus fibres are disturbed at the top. At the bottom and on the right side the original cutting lines are still visible. Between line 1 and 2 a large lacuna caused some loss of text and there are some worm holes that have damaged the text. There is a margin of 2 cm left blank at the top and sides of the papyrus suggesting this sheet was part of a codex."
