    {
      "label": "Further remarks",
      "value": "This undated text starts on the verso with nine lines and continues on the recto with eight lines. On the recto and the verso a line has been left blank at the same distance from the top. This blank line occurs on the recto between lines 2 and 3, on the verso between lines 1 and 2. The handwriting is the same on the verso and recto as can be concluded from some particularities in the script that occur on both sides. The k\u0101f in initial position has a hairpin shape. The alif in final position sometimes extends below the line. The ligature of the letters l\u0101m-alif occurs in the form of two oblique strokes connected at the bottom with a loop. This loop also occurs when the ligature is connected to a preceding letter. The ligature l\u0101m-alif is also occasionally written without a loop at the bottom."
    },
